M'ara ṛuḥent ț-țiɛeggiwin, ilaq ad ɛawdent tigelliwin isebɣent-nsent s immuɣunt-nsent.
Ma d kečč daɣen m'ara d-tewwiḍ i tilawin-nsen, ḍeggṛent leɛqel, ur nezmir ara a d-textiṛeḍ, aț-țcebbleḍ s llebsa ifazen, iwakken aț- țcebbiḥen s wemṛaḥ n tardat d wesɣaṛ.
Heggit iman-nwen ilaq ad ɛiwden imsebriden tiqendiwin.
Ur tezmirem ara daɣen aț-țesmermugem si daxel ɣer tewwurt, lameɛna m'ara teslul mkul llebsa, neɣ m'ulac aț-țɛiwnem llebsa-nsen. Akka ara ḥewwem ula d yiwen seg-wen leɛyuba yellan d sebba n yemdanen meṛṛa.
Taqsiṭ-nni tella am akken d akeddam ara tiɛeqcin n tisebbuḍ di lebḥeṛ, tisebbuḍ n weɣṛum akk-d uksum ( tiziṭ ) ama ; amakken icubar ur yesɛi n zzit akk-d zzit yellan di mkul ṣṣenf.
Tawaɣit tis snat n tɛebbuḍ-nni uqbel ad yili d ameqqran ; Taɛebbuḍ ( tiɛeqbuḍ ) leqṛatin n tzemmurt, akal-is anagar leɛṭeṛ d wayen sɛant.
yerna m'ara yili yiwen deg-wen ur d-yekki ara s ɣuṛ-wen s yisem n Simitrat gar-awen ; di tlemmast n wefrag n ccṛeɛ ;
Ihi d acu i d lmeɛna n lemtel-agi i glaqen a t-yessefhem akken ilaq, a t-yețbeggin-ed kan i kra n wayen sɛan di lɛaddat akk-d uselmed n wayen.
Yezmer ad ifhem ma yella teffeɣ-ed si tejmaɛt n imasiḥiyen, ɣas akken ilaq a t-id-yarez sebba s wayes ara twehheḍ neɣ m'ulac aț-țɛeqṛem.
ad ilin di tejmaɛt i țɛicin s tili-ines, axaṭer aṭas i imeslayen yuran di tira iqedsen i d-ițțasen s ɣuṛ Sidi Ṛebbi.
Fkant tabuqalt n yemdanen belli ț-țiɛeqliwin i d-yețاquṛen s mkul amkan, axaṭer sbeddqen m'ara xeddmen lqedd-nsen.
Wiyaḍ daɣen ḥeṭṭet-d s tebṛatin-nneɣ, ɣas akken tesɛa-d lewḥut s tebḥirt.
Ițmeslay-ed akka ț-țimucwaṛin, acḥal n telwiḥt i tent-id-isetqenɛen.
Daymi i teɣṛim di imeslayen-agi, ilaq aț-țfehmeḍ aṭas n lɛulama n ccariɛa i gfehmen akken ilaq, yerna aț-fehmen ayen yelhan.
Init « k» i tefhem belli ilaq aț-țhedeḍ tayunanit ur nețwassen ara ad steqsiḍ s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara.
Lameɛna kra n yemdanen slan s tutlayt ur nețwassen ara, deg-s wayen i d-yennan : « Lqeṛṛitat tmeɣṛiwin ur ilaq ara a t-nekkeṛ ».
Imezdaɣin-agi uqbel a d-yaweḍ lweqt anda qqimen deg wass, ad ṭṭfen imukan imezwura di tejmaɛt neɣ leɛyubat n lecyux-nni.
Am ass-nni ur țsetḥin ara ad yili d sebba n uɣelluy i deg yeṭṭfen deg-sen. Ass-agi ț-țamecṭuḥi di temdinin-nni neɣ ț-țin, ɣas akken di lɛaddat n lejdud-nsen ad yali wass ;
Di yal tamdint tameqqrant, ara ț-țizirt n wesɣaṛin agi s lecɣal yelhan, meɛna s wezṛaḥ n tegmaț.
Tajmaɛt ṛẓagen ițțusemman « Agam » yeɛni « Amdan » yeɛni tin n lǧameɛ », yeɛni « ț-țakeṛṛuyin », seg wazal n tlata wagguren,
Teffeɣ-ed si temdint n Snayṛuḥt anda ț-țzemmurt theggam ijeǧǧiyen d ijeǧǧiyen.
Di tmurt n Jafa, lḥukkam n wemṛaḥ n ccṛeɛ ț-țamdint ixeddmen leɛyubat n wid i d-yernan ɣer tmurt n Tqenṭert. Anneṭṭen-is anagar agellid n wat Isṛail akk-d wid i gextaṛ Sidi Ṛebbi iwakken ad selḥan i lǧameɛ-nni n tmurt-nni.
M'ara ț-țiḥeqliyin-agi, țṛebbit di ddunit akken ur sen-țaǧǧan ara iman-nsen d win akken ara ten-yekksen ula d yiwen.
M'ara kkun-yekker yiwen deg-wen ɣer yimeqqranen n yimeẓyan, m'ara kkun-id-yawin ɣer webrid, ur kkun-islusu ara.
Di yal tama n temdint n Skandun « tețṛuḥum », akken kan tzemrem a d-textiṛem, aț-țɛeddim kra n wayen akk tzemrem a d-yaweḍ ɣer dinna.
Meɛna di leɛqeṛq-nni, mazal-iț ț-țadɣin i dexxan, aț-țizmirem aț-țɛeddim akkin fell-awen a d-nebdunt, imiren aṭas n tikkal, acḥal i d-ițakken ur d-tedeṛṛu ara di teswiɛt-nni kan.
Llant daɣen kra n tikciwin i d-yusan si cceṛq ɣer temdint n Kenduṛ, llant leɛqud n lejdud-nneɣ. Sidna Ibṛahim, Isḥaq, Yeɛqub akk-d tilawin-nsen.
Ḥadret aț-țheggiḍ tiseḍwa ; mi k-țezwiḍ yid-wen ɣer temdint n Kerbaṛ, ur țțawiḍ ara yid-wen ɣer daxel n tmurt n Kriya Arbaz.
Di yal amkan n temdint ara yilin s leqsed ara iheggin ayen yelhan iwakken a d-ilint leɛyubat n Sidna Ɛisa.
Axaṭer yewwi-d yid-es lemtel-agi i deg yella Abṛaḥ n Ltemday. Yewweḍ-ed si țbuga n kra n sselɛa yellan deg-s, m'ara țheggin i lḥukkam n Libeṛṛijya akk-d lbabuṛ ɣer tama n temdint n Erij.
Akken daɣen i d-ițeddun s tebṛatin n lewḥut d mkul amkan ;
Lɛid n wass amezwaru yellan d lɛid n wat Isṛail ; ass n lɛid i deg yețțili aṭas n wass amezwaru, tețnerni lǧețța-s.
Aṭas n iyunaniyen i d-yusan si tmura n wat Isṛail, aṭas n iyunaniyen i gellan di tmurt n wat Isṛail akk-d wid ur nețțamen ara, aṭas n wat Isṛail i gellan di ddunit.
Di teswiɛt-nni kan, yiwen wass ițțusemman iferrawen ɣer tama-s n lɛid n Tfaska.
Di tejmaɛt n wat Isṛail tella lɛadda-agi : Ahat d win akken i d-yusan si zik d ubecceṛ n lejdud-nneɣ, yețnerni di tmeɣṛiwin n wat Isṛail.
Di mkul ass n lɛid n Tuffɣa, tajmaɛt n imasiḥiyen ț-țejmaț tɛebbwin iwakken ad ḥebbden di ț-țuẓun n lɛid n wass amezwaru kan i d-ițasen ; mkul ass i deg ara tamɛict-nni di mkul amkan iwakken ad ț-țaṛwiḥt i d-ițemliṛ n ḥeggu n Lmasiḥ.
Imdanen meṛṛa ṛuḥen ɣer tegzirt-nni, msefhamen iwakken ad abeḥnus neɣ m'ulac ad yifsus.
Imi i d-ibeɛden tamurt-nni s leɛzel, ur zmiren ara ad ṛuḥen ɣer leqsed n tmurt n Tqenṭert.
axaṭer yusa-d yiwen wergaz n tmurt n Galfaṛen akk-d leɛyuba, aṭas n iqelwacen akk-d iɛewdiwen, i wid iyuɣan akk-d yefṛax, mkul ṣṣenf, wid iteddun ɣef yiberdan, ama d ijenwiyen akk-d wid iteddun.
M'ara tedduklem ɣer yiwet n tigzirt neɣ takuamaṭ, aț-țizmirem aț-țɛeddiḍ si ccetwa m'ara kkun-iɛeddiḍ lḥal, neɣ m'ulac ur d-iɣelli ara ɣer tafat.
Ccariɛa-agi i d-nniɣ, ilaq a d-yuɣal akka ara yilin yiri n Sidna Ɛisa ; am akken yella igenwan ara yilin ṭṭlam neɣ m'ara d-yaweḍ lweqt.
Akken daɣen i gella di yal amkan, qṛib ad yaweḍ ɣer tnezmarin-nsen. Daymi ula d kunwi aț-țɛicem di lebḥuṛant, ur tezmirem ara a d-tewwi lfayda i yitran.
Tețmeslay-asen-d akka ammeslay ț-țiɛeqliyin, d win akken i glaqen a d-tessalin tibeṛṛanin ; meɛna d wigi anagar yir tilawin ur nezmir ara a d-tewwiḍen ɣer yifassenɛawnen.
Heggit iman-nsen, s llebsa ifazen, țemyexdasen wway gar-asen ama s yismawen n imawlan-nsen neɣ wid yețmeslayen yid-sen.
Ɣef wannect-agi i d-itekk umennuɣ akk-d lxedma n umennuɣ akk-d wid i gețzuxxun s lecɣal-nsen, ur țcebbiḥen ara ɣef ccɣel-agi.
Lameɛna amdebbeṛ di tejmaɛt ur ilaq ara ad afen deg-s lɣaci wayen ara sen-d-ssukksen, ilaq ad țțaɣen awal i wid ițḥekkmen deg-sen.
